  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, technical feasibility, and initial
      effectiveness (i.e., weight loss primarily measured as percent excess weight loss) of TGVR
      performed using the Bard RESTORe Suturing System
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
